I '''Pramoedya Ananta Toer'''<ref>[[Javanese people|Javanese]] do not have [[surname]]s in the Western sense. ''Toer'' is not Pramoedya's family name, and usually he is formally addressed as only ''Mr Pramoedya''.</ref> ([[6 Febreru]] [[1925]] – [[30 Abril]] [[2006]]) metung yang [[Indonesia]]n a talasulat da reng novel, makuyad a salita, salese (''essay''), [[:en:polemic|polemic]] ampong amlat ning kayang bangsa ampo ing kayang lahi. Masasaklo la kareng kayang obra deng panaun ning pamaniakup, ing pamagalsa ning ning Indonesia para king katimawan, ing pamaglub da reng Hapones aniang Kaduang Gerang Pangyatu, ampo reng rehimen da ri [[Sukarno]] ampong [[Suharto]] kaibat ning panaun ning pamaniakup, at luluban no ning kasalesayan nang pangsarili ampong pambangsa.

Neng kai, e ra la kapad deng kapanibalan da reng talasakup ampong tubung kapamahalan deng kasulatan nang Pramoedya. Kabang daragul ing kasikatan na king kilual ning Indonesia kanitang panaung e pa miliari ing pamagbayu (''pre-reformation''). Aniang minalis king rehimen nang [[Suharto]], mirasan ya king pamanaliwa king kabilian ning pulitica ampong pamipate-pate para king upaya king Indonesia. Uling king paglalawe kayang antimong mitagan ibat king sadiang rehimen (lipat ning linaban ya murin karela), dakal deng banuang nigse king isla ning [[Buru]], nung nu ro susukul deng presung pampulitica, at nung nu ne kinuentu ing pikabaluan nang diling obra, ing [[Buru Quartet]]. King pamagsalita ya mu o kuentung mirake kareng aliwang presu ing epicung iti, bayu ya misulat at pasalikut a pepalual. Linaban ya i Toer kareng patakaran ning mumunang pamuntuk (i [[Sukarno]]) ampo ing kayang kayalili, ing rehimen nang ''New Order'' (o Bayung Palakad) ning Pamuntuk o Presidenti [[Suharto]], dapot pinu at e halata ing kayang pamagpuna, dapot masikan ing kayang pamalak laban king colonialismu ampong discriminaciun basi king lahi (''racism''). Aniang dakal a banuang atiu king sukulan ampong mekulung ya king kayang bale (''house arrest''), megi yang kilalang sagisag ning katimawan ning pamipahayag ampo king katulirang pantau. 

